github的https换为ssh

URL: https://blog.csdn.net/github_37538357/article/details/60468050

1.git remote -v
查看当前地址

2.git remote set-url origin git@github.com:<<USERNAME>>/<<OTHERREPOSITROY>>.git设置为ssh地址

3.git remote -v
修改完成后查看地址，配置为ssh地址就正确了


关于ssh连接主机，git连接github失败的问题：ssh -T git@github.com&&Permission denied (publickey)
URL： https://blog.csdn.net/sunnypotter/article/details/18948053/

解决方案 git@github.com出现Permission denied (publickey)
URL: https://blog.csdn.net/samxx8/article/details/51497004

具体形式：
Host github.com
	User git
	HostName github.com
	PreferredAuthentications publickey
	IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa_fengjia_snerdi